		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [2.88]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=TheGreatSieg&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>You can do a DoN mission and a task at the same time.&nbsp;&nbsp;That is how you can get crystals too.  Next time try doing a mission for the zone for whatever task you are working on.  <br><br>e.g. You can do the collect 6 drake bloods task while doing the mission &quot;Grounding the drakes&quot; and get crystals for the mission and the rewards for the task.  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Sieger<br><br>Lv 70 Druid <br>Xegony server</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
