f the tasks?  Perhaps do one easy one over and over til faction is up as gbajj mentioned?  Or is it just better(faster) to get a group together and tackle em that way?</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
